				Détails sur l'adoption 
					<span class="material-icons">pets</span>
				</p>
			</div>
           	<div class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:flex-row">
                <figure class="flex flex-col max-w-xl p-4">
                    <div class="rounded-md border-8 border-green-blue max-w-xl ">
                        <img class="w-full" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6864965/pexels-photo-6864965.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=1&w=500" alt="dog-cat-home">
